#######
#ingame
#######

^#5aa9d6;Lets go kill cactaur!^reset;

This mod removes all other starting outfit options in favor of the tier 1 armor of that race. Works for Vanilla races only.

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

######
#steam
######

[h1]Lets go kill cactaur![/h1]
This version of the mod adds the tier 1 armor of every race to every races starting outfit option. Works for Vanilla races only.

